		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I made a version that lets you choose between different built-in rules or choose your own, and has a grid that's 64x32 instead of 32x32. Otherwise it's pretty much the same:<br /><br /><img src="http://nova.themonkeybob.net/rsc/conway6432.png" alt="Image" /><br /><br />There's a known bug about having the cursor on the leftmost column because it doesn't bother to have a special case to fix that, but I don't think it should be a big issue.<br /><br /><a href="http://novasquirrel.com/dl/Life64x32.zip" class="postlink">Download (with source)</a>

		

